 React a Component jotota na beshi important, tar cheye beshi important State.





 pubsub : publish subscribe pattern

 state ekta observer variable, ei variable er sathe kichu listener, event jukto kora ase.

 kono vabe state poriborton hole, jara er subscriber ase tara update pabe. 
 kono na kono component ase je component gulo ei state ta ke change korbe.


 State hocche component er actual data, state ta hocche data store.

 Ei state ke poriborton korar jonno bivinno function/method create korte hoy. 
 Ei function gulo hocche amader publisher.
 Ei state er vitor jsx er code gulo hocche subscriber.


 Constructor er vitor state neya jay.

 React er vitor je state ache oita kintu javascript er object.
 variable o bolechi, karon state abar class er property. obserable property, jeita change hole notification pabo.


 Developer er chita ta ke puro data upor niye jete hobe. 
 UI kemon hobe, data structure kemon hobe.


 1:04:38 


 primitive data hocche muteable.

 javascript er vasay je kono array/object muteable data.


 component toiri korar somoy 2 ta jinish mathay rakhte hobe.
 1. Konta dummy component hobe
 2. konta smart component hobe



 javascript a funtion hocche first class value.

 variable ke props akare jevabe pass kore,
 function/value ke sei vabe pass kore.